Package affix.java.project.moneyservice

Class MoneyServiceIO

  • java.lang.Object
    • affix.java.project.moneyservice.MoneyServiceIO
  • public class MoneyServiceIO
extends java.lang.Object
    This class acts as a bridge between Money Service Site and Money Service HQ. It handles input and output files related to Money Service application. It is used to serialize and de-serialize Site reports containing daily transactions. It is used to store the Box of Cash from Site in a text file. NB! To store files in a specific directory the file name needs to include the path to that directory.
